Mitchells & Butlers Plc (MAB)  investor  Joe Lewis  may have boosted his stake in the company last week to
more than 25 percent, allowing him to block resolutions by the
company or other investors, the  Sunday Times  reported, without
saying how it obtained the information.  Some fund managers, including Legal & General Group Plc,
sold shares in the pub group last week, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
